      "description": "Overseer Task Viewer",
      "context": "Local webapp for visualizing Overseer task store state.\n\n**Problem:** Agents using Overseer via MCP have no visual way to inspect task store state.\n\n**Goals:**\n- At-a-glance task hierarchy visualization\n- Visual dependency graph (blockedBy edges)\n- Quick edits without CLI syntax\n\n**Tech Stack:**\n- CLI: Rust `os ui` command\n- API: Hono (type-safe RPC via `hc<AppType>()`)\n- Frontend: Astro (static) + React islands\n- UI: shadcn/ui, dark theme\n- Graph: @xyflow/react + dagre\n- Data: TanStack Query (5s polling)\n- Styling: Tailwind CSS v4\n\n**Package Structure:**\n```\nui/\n├── server/     # Hono API\n├── web/        # Astro frontend\n└── shared/     # Shared types\n```\n\n**Critical Path:** D2 (API) -> D3 (Shell) -> D5 (Graph) -> Integration\n\n**Effort:** L-XL (3-5 days)",
